node.text: We recently teamed up with Chef Edward Lee's @leeinitiative to bring a spark back to communities across the country, with a little help from the e-tron Sportback. Reaching over 68 farms and 74 restaurants and non-profits across the country, The LEE Initiative's Restaurant Reboot Relief program is helping to sustain local food economies and the communities they feed. We visited four of these businesses with Chef Lee to learn more about their stories and see how they are staying resilient while adapting to the changing needs of their communities.

node.title: Audi Presents: Bringing the Spark Back to Communities with Lee Initiative

node.text: On July 16th, we collaborated with @Kehlani for a magical, socially-distanced, drive-in concert celebrating LA’s essential workers. To all of the heroes out there on the frontlines, thanks for everything you do.
